[{"ave_id":"AVE-2006-0005","file_name":"2006/AVE-2006-0005.toml","cve_id":"CVE-2006-6565","title":"FileZilla Server 通配符参数 NULL 指针解引用拒绝服务漏洞","description":"FileZilla Server 0.9.22 之前版本在处理 LIST 和 NLST 命令的通配符参数时存在空指针解引用漏洞。远程未经认证的攻击者可通过向 FTP 服务端发送特制的包含通配符参数的 LIST 或 NLST 命令，触发空指针解引用导致服务崩溃，造成拒绝服务。该漏洞影响 FileZilla Server 0.9.21 及更早版本，CVSS 评分 4.0，危害等级中危。用户需升级至 0.9.22 或更高版本修复此漏洞。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":4.0,"aliases":["CVE-2006-6565"],"sources":["nuclei"],"published":"2006-12-15T11:28:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T22:33:22.903","remediation":"升级 FileZilla Server 至 0.9.22 及以上版本，该版本已修复 LIST/NLST 命令通配符参数导致的空指针解引用问题。若无法立即升级，可在防火墙或 IPS 中过滤包含通配符的 FTP LIST/NLST 命令，或限制仅信任 IP 访问 FTP 服务作为临时缓解措施。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-15T00:00:00Z","references":["http://sourceforge.net/project/shownotes.php?release_id=470364&group_id=21558","http://www.vupen.com/english/advisories/2006/4937","https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/30853","https://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/2914","https://github.com/projectdiscovery/nuclei-templates/blob/main/network/cves/2006/CVE-2006-6565.yaml","https://github.com/trickest/cve/blob/a90de4f84b4783951362f491671e1e9decfc17cb/2006/CVE-2006-6565.md","https://github.com/projectdiscovery/nuclei-templates/blob/69a5a3cf926251a00061ec14d208b227367df73d/network/cves/2006/CVE-2006-6565.yaml","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/8aea42c71147e21c6d32b71ffce877107de995c6/cves/2006/6xxx/CVE-2006-6565.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-2006/CVE-2006-6565","https://github.com/adampielak/nuclei-templates/blob/ac9605f5a915670fd80cb4e1904f4435f1835b65/nuclei-v3/C/CVE-2006-6565_3.yaml","https://github.com/youki992/VscanPlus/blob/714a0e276a538a22c1a6215c71458a8b59a920ef/pocs_yml/nucleiFiles/network/cves/2006/CVE-2006-6565.yaml","https://github.com/mabitoski/cve_submodules/blob/44ad7e2705b3aef1b2ffaf64bd47596c10a6c2e4/2006/CVE-2006-6565.md","https://github.com/github/ad