003.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-2006-0002","file_name":"2006/AVE-2006-0002.toml","cve_id":"CVE-2006-2173","title":"FileZilla FTP Server 缓冲区溢出导致拒绝服务与代码执行漏洞","description":"FileZilla FTP Server 2.2.22 存在缓冲区溢出漏洞，远程认证攻击者可通过发送超长的 PORT 或 PASS 命令后跟 MLSD 命令触发该漏洞，导致目标 FTP 服务进程崩溃造成拒绝服务，甚至可能执行任意代码。该漏洞影响 FileZilla FTP Server 2.2.22 版本，CVSS 评分 6.4，危害等级中危。目前厂商已发布修复版本。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":6.4,"aliases":["CVE-2006-2173"],"sources":["nuclei"],"published":"2006-05-04T12:38:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T22:24:28.800","remediation":"升级 FileZilla Server 至 0.9.29 及以上版本（此漏洞已在后续版本修复）。如无法升级，在防火墙中限制对 FTP 端口（默认 21）的访问 IP，仅允许受信任 IP 连接，并对 FTP 用户实施严格的命令长度限制。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-15T00:00:00Z","references":["http://archives.neohapsis.com/archives/bugtraq/2006-05/0139.html","http://marc.info/?l=bugtraq&m=114658586018818&w=2","http://www.infigo.hr/en/in_focus/tools","http://www.infigo.hr/hr/in_focus/advisories/INFIGO-2006-05-03","http://www.osvdb.org/25221","http://www.securityfocus.com/bid/17802","https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/26303","https://github.com/projectdiscovery/nuclei-templates/blob/main/network/cves/2006/CVE-2006-2173.yaml","https://github.com/trickest/cve/blob/a90de4f84b4783951362f491671e1e9decfc17cb/2006/CVE-2006-2173.md","https://github.com/projectdiscovery/nuclei-templates/blob/69a5a3cf926251a00061ec14d208b227367df73d/network/cves/2006/CVE-2006-2173.yaml","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/8aea42c71147e21c6d32b71ffce877107de995c6/cves/2006/2xxx/CVE-2006-2173.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-2006/CVE-2006-2173","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/e64e866f5c799abe7f39eba36818200f3831f1cb/CVE/data/2006/CVE-2006-2173.json","https://github.com/mabitoski/cve_submodules/blob/44ad7e2705b3aef1b2ffaf64bd47596c10a6c2e4/2006/CVE-2006-2173.md","https://github.com/adampielak/nuclei-templates/blob/ac9605f5a915670fd80cb4e1904f4435f1835b65/nuclei-v3/C/C