es/blob/69a5a3cf926251a00061ec14d208b227367df73d/http/cves/2006/CVE-2006-1681.yaml","https://github.com/sepehrdaddev/zap-scripts/blob/2b63b02ca79cc7f0023cdbab72c5c6c774354b07/active/CVE-2006-1681.js","https://github.com/lianqingsec/NucleiPocGather/blob/dcce204f62196117b9c95c52d8101ccf7a5d27bc/poc/cve/CVE-2006-1681_5.yaml","https://github.com/adampielak/nuclei-templates/blob/ac9605f5a915670fd80cb4e1904f4435f1835b65/nuclei-v2/C/CVE-2006-1681.yaml","https://github.com/rix4uni/nucleihub-templates/blob/579a0234551b9e0e322460a62dc77bd6109e4aff/nucleihub-templates/CVE-2006-1681_4.yaml","https://github.com/itsmenaga/Nuclei-Templates-All/blob/7e93c24e44969db15f4072e1c6a322a026452d6b/Vulnerability-Templates/cve-2006-1681-1325.yaml","https://github.com/ExpLangcn/NucleiTP/blob/2b7ecb9031a6eda4f272793045f29b339d8e0cce/CVES/medium/cve-2006-1681-1323.yaml","https://github.com/0xelixer/new/blob/6f6dd4a43a76ce74c1e8cc0558629a2ea198286e/nuclei-temps/cent/template1/cve-2006-1681-1327.yaml","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/8aea42c71147e21c6d32b71ffce877107de995c6/cves/2006/1xxx/CVE-2006-1681.json"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/2006/AVE-2006-0001.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-2006-0004","file_name":"2006/AVE-2006-0004.toml","cve_id":"CVE-2006-3392","title":"Webmin 及 Usermin 任意文件读取漏洞","description":"Webmin 1.290 之前版本及 Usermin 1.220 之前版本中存在路径遍历漏洞。由于 simplify_path 函数在 HTML 解码之前被调用，远程攻击者无需认证即可利用 \"%01\" 等编码字符绕过 \"../\" 过滤检查，通过构造特制的 \"..%01\" 序列读取服务器上的任意文件，导致敏感信息泄露。该漏洞影响 Webmin <1.290 及 Usermin <1.220 版本，无需特殊权限即可利用。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":5.0,"aliases":["CVE-2006-3392"],"sources":["cve"],"published":"2006-07-06","updated":"2026-06-16","remediation":"升级 Webmin 至 1.290 及以上版本，Usermin 至 1.220 及以上版本。Debian 用户执行 `apt-get update && apt-get upgrade webmin usermin`，Gentoo 用户同步 Portage 并更新相应包。临时缓解措施：在防火墙上限制对 Webmin（默认 10000 端口）和 Usermin（默认 20000 端口）的管理地址白名单访问。","stat